							<h3 class="header">Privacy Policy</h3>
							<p class="content">As a valued Customer, you are entitled to
								your personal privacy. With that in mind, Starmart Express has
								adopted a Privacy Policy (“Policy”) which explains and confirms
								our commitment to provide you with a variety of travel services
								while maintaining your personal privacy.</p>

							<h3 class="header">Sharing & Disclosure of Personal
								Information</h3>
							<p class="content">Starmart Express will never sell your
								personal or financial information to any third party. Your
								personal and/or financial information, however, may be shared
								with third parties, who are authorized by Starmart Express for
								the following purposes:</p>
							<ul class="page-list">
								<li>Credit card verification, processing and fraud
									detection purposes as part of your ticket purchase; and/or</li>
								<li>Legal disclosure to a governmental agency, law
									enforcement or court as required by law in the good faith
									belief that disclosure is necessary or advisable.</li>
							</ul>

							<p class="content">Starmart Express uses third party payment
								processing companies to bill you for goods and services, or for
								other purposes within the ordinary course of business. We make
								these companies commit to contract (1) to provide protections
								for your personally identifiable information that are no less
								protective than those set out in this Policy, and (2) to use
								your personally identifying information only for the purposes
								for which the third party has been engaged by Starmart Express.
								Starmart Express is not liable for the acts or omissions of
								these third parties except to the extent required by applicable
								law.</p>
							<p class="content">
								In addition, if you decide to participate in our marketing
								programs (including but not limited to customer loyalty,
								incentives, affinity, promotions or contests), your
								non-financial personal information may be released to reputable
								third parties in order to fulfill certain business requirements
								of those programs. <br />We may also share information that we
								collect in the aggregate with third parties, including, without
								limitation, our marketing partners.
							</p>

							<h3 class="header">Personal Information Collected For
								Processing Transactions</h3>
							<p class="content">Starmart Express collects personal
								information (name, address, phone number, identification number,
								passport number etc.) as well as a credit card number to process
								transactions. An e-mail address for an online purchase is
								optional; however, your e-mail address is required for Print at
								Home purchases and if you would like a copy of your confirmation
								statement e-mailed to you. We use the information we collect
								during the purchase process for billing purposes, to fill your
								orders, for administrative, analytical, correspondence, and
								operational purposes, to customize advertisements and offers and
								for other marketing purposes, and for other purposes discussed
								in this Policy.</p>

							<h3 class="header">Marketing Programs</h3>
							<p class="content">Starmart Express collects personal
								information including email addresses and telephone numbers to
								facilitate our marketing programs and communicate with customers
								who have expressed an interest in upcoming specials, discounts,
								and helpful travel tips. Often this information is collected on
								web sites that are hosted by companies associated with Starmart
								Express. Unless you choose to opt-in, your information will not
								be shared.</p>
							<p class="content">By participating in our marketing
								programs, you agree to honor and abide by the rules and
								regulations contained therein. Please read all rules before
								participating.</p>
							<p class="content">Starmart Express takes no responsibility
								for the specific privacy rules or terms and conditions of the
								contest sponsors or other third parties and we encourage you to
								examine the privacy policies contained on these sites.</p>
							<b class="subheader">Rewards Program</b>
							<p class="content">If you do not already have a Rewards
								account, you can easily establish one by visiting our website.
								Electing to establish a Rewards account will enroll you in the
								Starmart Express frequent rider program and give you the
								opportunity to earn rewards. You will not be able to earn points
								toward reward trips if you elect to not sign up for this
								program. As a Rewards Member, you may also receive special
								offers by e-mail simply for being a Member of the Rewards
								program.</p>
							<p class="content">We may use the personally identifiable
								information you provide when you become a Rewards Member for
								analytical, administrative, marketing, correspondence or other
								operational or business purposes. For more information on how we
								may use your personally identifiable information as a Rewards
								Member, please see our Customer Communications section below.</p>

							<h3 class="header">Customer Communications</h3>
							<b class="subheader">Post Purchase E-mail Communication</b>
							<p class="content">When you make a travel reservation with us
								and you provide your e-mail address during the purchase process,
								we may send you trip-related emails, including, without
								limitation, emails that (a) confirm the details of your
								purchase, (b) describe service-related information in connection
								with your reservation or to inform you of upgrades or product
								enhancements related to your purchase, (c) request feedback on
								our services and/or your specific travel experiences, or (d)
								include special offers for products or services from Starmart
								Express or our marketing partners related to your trip.</p>

							<b class="subheader">E-mail Promotions, Offers, and Updates</b>
							<p class="content">You may receive e-mail communications from
								us which may include special offers, Rewards information or
								similar offerings. You may opt-out of receiving these messages
								at any time by selecting “unsubscribe” from any email
								communication.</p>

							<p class="content">As a Member of the Rewards program, you
								may receive Rewards e-mail communications, which may include
								program news and special offers, either during the Rewards
								enrolment process or from your Rewards account preferences web
								page. During enrolment, the default option is to receive both
								Rewards e-mail products. If you are not interested in receiving
								these messages with special Members-only news and offers, the
								boxes should be unchecked prior to submitting the enrolment
								form. You may also opt-out of receiving these messages at any
								time by adjusting your preferences through the account
								preferences webpage.</p>

							<b class="subheader">Account Information</b>
							<p class="content">We currently send non-promotional e-mails
								to our Rewards Members containing account and award status
								notifications, to notify Members of program updates, and to
								communicate other program-related information.</p>

							<b class="subheader">Customer Feedback</b>
							<p class="content">We like to hear from our Customers and
								encourage you to e-mail us your comments, questions or other
								feedback. By submitting such information along with your e-mail
								address, you consent to receiving e-mail from us in response to
								your feedback or question.</p>

							<b class="subheader">Contests & Surveys</b>
							<p class="content">We may occasionally offer users the
								opportunity to participate in surveys or contests on our web
								site.</p>
							<p class="content">If we have your e-mail address, we may
								also send you surveys or contest invitations by e-mail. We may
								have your e-mail address if:</p>
							<ul class="page-list">
								<li>You have made a purchase on our web site and provided
									your e-mail address during the purchase process;</li>
								<li>You have set up a Rewards account and provided your
									e-mail address either during the registration process or when
									updating your account information;</li>
								<li>You provide a friend’s e-mail address when you refer
									the friend to one of our web pages; or</li>
								<li>We have received your e-mail address by any other
									means.</li>
							</ul>

							<p class="content">If you choose to participate in a contest
								or survey, we may request certain personally identifiable
								information from you. This information may include contact
								information (such as name, e-mail address, phone number, and
								shipping address) and optional demographic information (such as
								your age and gender).</p>
							<p class="content">Participation in these surveys or contests
								is completely voluntary and you have a choice whether or not to
								disclose this information. We may use this information to
								administer the contest or survey (e.g., notify contest winners,
								award prizes, and update participant’s profiles). We may also
								use this information to improve the web site experience for our
								Customers, to improve our product or service offerings, or for
								other internal business uses.</p>
							<p class="content">We may use third party service providers
								to conduct these surveys or contests. These companies are
								prohibited from using our users’ personally identifiable
								information for any other purpose. These third parties are bound
								by contract to Starmart Express to use adequate security
								measures to protect your personal information.</p>

							<b class="subheader">Forward-to-a-Friend and Refer-a-Friend</b>
							<p class="content">You may use a referral feature (either on
								a web page, in an e-mail, from a banner ad or other
								communication) to inform a friend about a Starmart Express web
								page or promotion. Starmart Express may use any e-mail address
								provided when using this referral feature to send an e-mail on
								your behalf to such designated recipients about the particular
								promotion, product, or service in which you indicated your
								"friend" may have an interest.</p>

							<b class="subheader">Site Usage Profile</b>
							<p class="content">We store and use certain personally
								identifiable information and information that we collect through
								cookies and log files to create a site usage profile of your
								preferences. We may use this information to provide you with
								targeted advertisements and offers on our web site. In addition
								we may provide this information to our select marketing
								platforms, and these cookies may be used for targeted online
								advertising by both Starmart Express and third party merchants
								on third party websites.</p>

							<h3 class="header">Non-Personally-Identifiable Information
								We Collect</h3>
							<p class="content">In some cases, Starmart Express may
								collect information about you that is not personally
								identifiable. Examples of this type of information include, but
								are not limited to the frequency of your use of this web site
								and the route by which you choose to access it, and your use of
								any hyperlinks available on this web site. We and our service
								providers or agents may process and use this data for purposes
								including, but not limited to planning web site development,
								assessing patterns of use, planning and assessing marketing
								initiatives by Starmart Express. This information is gathered by
								certain tools and methods such as the collection of your IP
								address or the use of cookies.</p>

							<ul class="page-list">
								<li><b class="subheader">IP Addresses</b><br /> An
									Internet Protocol ("IP") address is a numeric code, for
									example, "201.136.720.186." This code is used to communicate
									between your Internet service provider and the World Wide Web.
									An IP address does not identify you individually. Starmart
									Express logs inbound IP addresses to administer our website and
									to aggregate information on site traffic for internal use.</li>
								<li><b class="subheader">Cookies</b><br /> Cookies (and
									similar files such as single pixel GIF’s, web beacons or tags)
									are small computer files written to your computer when you
									visit websites. You have the option of setting your browser to
									refuse Cookies. To utilize all promotional offers and discounts
									on Starmart Express sites you need to allow temporary "session
									cookies" that will go away when your browser is closed. No
									personal or credit card information is collected by any
									Starmart Express sites Cookies. <br /> <br /> Starmart
									Express sites Cookies collect anonymous, non-personal
									information to make your use of the web site easier and to
									allow Starmart Express to track and improve the effectiveness
									of our on-line advertising. For example, when you check the
									appropriate box a Starmart Express Cookie will remember your
									origination and destination locations. <br /> <br /> Starmart
									Express also works with on-line advertising agencies to sell
									Starmart Express 's services. These agencies use Cookies to
									track which Starmart Express ads you have seen and the amounts
									you spend on Starmart Express sites so that we may effectively
									market to consumers.</li>
							</ul>

							<h3 class="header">Opt-Out Policy</h3>
							<p class="content">You have the option of being excluded from
								the various marketing contact lists by opting out at any time.
								Opt-out requests for contests, however, must be received within
								the duration of the contest to be removed from that contest. To
								stop messages coming to your cell phone, just reply "STOP."</p>
							<p class="content">
								To opt out, update or change any contact information send us an
								e-mail to <a href='mailto:webmaster@busticketonline.com'>webmaster@busticketonline.com</a>
								with your name, e-mail address and mailing address.
							</p>

							<h3 class="header">Security</h3>
							<p class="content">Starmart Express takes precautions to
								protect your personal and credit card information from misuse or
								unauthorized disclosure. For example, Starmart Express uses
								encryption software from VeriSign, the industry leader in secure
								site software technologies, to protect your information.</p>
							<p class="content">Look for the "s" after "http" in the
								address line of your browser. This indicates that the
								information sent from your computer to Starmart Express sites is
								encrypted using Secure Socket Layer (SSL) technology.</p>

							<h3 class="header">Links to Other Websites</h3>
							<p class="content">
								While we strive to partner with reputable firms, Starmart
								Express takes no responsibility for any content, information
								collected, terms and conditions or privacy rules maintained on
								any linked site and we strongly encourage you to examine the
								privacy policies contained on these sites. Please inform us at <a
									href='mailto:webmaster@busticketonline.com'>webmaster@busticketonline.com</a>
								about any concerns you may have regarding any of our linked
								sites.
							</p>

							<h3 class="header">Application of Policy</h3>
							<p class="content">This Policy is applicable to Starmart
								Express and its affiliates, including without limitation
								Starmart Express Sdn Bhd (Malaysia), Starmart Express Air Asia
								Liner Pte Ltd (Singapore), Rewards and all official Starmart
								Express offerings, divisions and departments, including without
								limitation Fare and Scheduling, Passenger Call Centre,
								Marketing, Customer Relations/Service, Rewards, and our mobile
								applications. Certain affiliated Starmart Express websites may
								also have additional privacy policies and procedures in place,
								as described on those websites.</p>

							<h3 class="header">Consent</h3>
							<p class="content">Your use of Starmart Express's website(s),
								services and participation in our marketing programs is your
								express consent for Starmart Express to use your personal
								information as described above. We reserve the right to make
								changes to this Policy from time to time, and for this reason,
								we encourage you to review the Policy posted at
								busticketonline.com, starmartonline.com periodically.</p>

							<h3 class="header">Changes in Privacy Policy</h3>
							<p class="content">This privacy policy is current as of the
								effective date set forth below. Starmart Express reserves the
								right to change this privacy policy from time to time consistent
								with applicable privacy laws and principles. If we make changes
								to this Policy, we will notify you by publication here.</p>

							<h3 class="header">Contact Us</h3>
